<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<title>無標題文件</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/reset.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/hero.css">
<script src="js/jquery-1.10.2.min.js"></script>
<script src="js/auto-full-height.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
<div id="content" _height="auto">
  <div id="intro">
    <h2>超級特務英雄榜</h2>
    <p>不是英雄不上榜，每一枚榮譽勳章，都代表您已挑戰自我，累積過人實力，<br>
      恭喜各位超級特務晉升英雄等級！<br>
      還沒取得榮譽勳章的特務可別洩氣，趕快掌握關鍵訊息再次挑戰！<br><br>
      <a href="/downloads?link=http%3A%2F%2Fdownload.microsoft.com%2Fdownload%2FA%2F0%2FD%2FA0D4CF2B-9B70-4846-A18D-0765D1F75343%2FMDT2012DeploymentWindows8.pdf" target="_blank"><img src="images/hero-bt.png" width="315" height="45" /></a></p>
  </div>
  
  

  <div id="article">
<% if !@myRecord.nil? %>
    <div class="<%= get_rank( @myRecord ) %> self">
      <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <tr>
          <td class="rank" align="center"><%= @myRank %></td>
          <td class="info"><p><b><%= @myRecord.name %></b><br>
            時間 : <%= ( @myRecord.time/60 ).floor %>分<%= @myRecord.time % 60 %>秒     分數 : <%= ( (100*@myRecord.score/15)).floor %>分<br>
            成功救援：<%= @myRecord.score %>人</p></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
<% end %>
    <hr></hr>
 
 <% i = params[:page].nil? ? 1 : (params[:page].to_i() -1) * 10 %>
<% @records.each do |record| %>
    <div class="<%= get_rank( record ) %>">
    	<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
        <tr>
          <td class="rank" align="center"><%= i %></td>
          <td class="info"><p><b><%= record.name %></b><br>
            時間 : <%= ( record.time/60 ).floor %>分<%= record.time % 60 %>秒     分數 : <%= ( (100 * record.score/15)).floor %>分<br>
            成功救援：<%= record.score %>人</p></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </div>
<% i += 1 %>
<% end %>

<%= paginate @records, :outter_window => 3 %>
 <!--div id="page"> <a href="#">&lt;</a><a href="#" class="active">1</a><a href="#">2</a><a href="#">3</a><a href="#">4</a><a href="#">5</a><a href="#">&gt;</a> </div-->

</div>
<!--content-->


